'''阿勃参'''（{{lang-xm|Commiphora gileadensis}}）是[[橄榄科|橄榄科]][[没药树属|没药树属]]灌木，原产[[阿拉伯半岛|阿拉伯半岛]]与[[东非|东非]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=''Commiphora gileadensis'' (L.) C.Chr.|url=http://powo.science.kew.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:127663-1|accessdate=2021-02-23|work=Plants of the World Online|publisher=Kew Science|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924053049/http://powo.science.kew.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:127663-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>其树脂可能是西方古籍记载的基列香脂（{{lang-en|Balm of Gilead}}）、麦加香膏（{{lang-en|Mecca balsam}}）。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=「阿勃參」與「拔爾撒摩」——中外藥物交流之長時段考察例證|author=陳明|url=https://fh.pku.edu.cn/docs/2018-11/20181120000405450765.pdf|date=2016-09-01|journal=漢學研究|issue=3|volume=34|page=161–203}}</ref>

== 词源 ==
《[[酉阳杂俎|酉阳杂俎]]》记载：“阿勃参，出拂林国。长一丈馀，皮色青白。叶细，两两相对。花似蔓菁，正黄。子似胡椒，赤色。斫其枝，汁如油，以涂疥癣，无不瘥者。其油极贵，价重于金。”据[[劳费尔|劳费尔]]考证，阿勃参一名很可能来自[[阿拉姆语|阿拉姆语]]单词{{lang|la|''afursama''}}，与英语单词{{lang|en|balsam}}同源。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Sino-Iranica: Chinese Contributions to the History of Civilization in Ancient Iran|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/29782155|last=Laufer|first=Berthold|date=1919|journal=Publications of the Field Museum of Natural History. Anthropological Series|issue=3|volume=15|pages=i, iii-iv, 185-597, 599-630|issn=0894-8380|access-date=2021-02-23|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117223750/https://www.jstor.org/stable/29782155|dead-url=no}}</ref>

